c: 42
v: 24
t: Jikheun dum le jih jipeuna-peuna Haba duseuta jikheun keu Allah Meunyo Neukheundak Allah Taʻala Lam ate gata Neucap bek teuhah Nyang bateu salah bandum Neusampoh Tinggai nyang neutroh nyanggot-got leupah Neumeung peubeuna nyang keubenaran Deungon Qur'an kalimah Allah Peue nyang lam dada bandum Neuteupue Hana meusapeue pih na meuilah